comments: Gordon (HOU) and Ingram (NOP) briefly engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Alvarado (NOP) establishes himself in Garuba's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Williamson (NOP) bobbles the hand-off pass from Nance Jr. (NOP) without any illegal contact occurring by Smith Jr. (HOU).
Alvarado (NOP) and Porter Jr. (HOU) mutually engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Alvarado (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as he defends Porter Jr. (HOU) during the drive.
Porter Jr. (HOU) gathers on his right foot and takes a step before putting the ball back on the floor while stumbling through the lane. A travel is correctly called prior to the release of his shot.
Alvarado (NOP) establishes himself in Garuba's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Gordon (HOU) adjusts to Ingram's (NOP) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the start of the drive.
Smith Jr. (HOU) initiates contact with McCollum's (NOP) wrist, which affects his SQBR as he attempts to make the pass.
Porter Jr. (HOU) avoids making contact with Nance Jr. (NOP) while contesting the dunk attempt.
Ingram (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as he defends Porter Jr. (HOU).
Jones (NOP) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Ingram (NOP) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Green's (HOU) arm.
Nance Jr. (NOP) and Smith Jr. (HOU) come together and marginal contact occurs as they jostle for rebounding position.
Porter Jr. (HOU) establishes himself outside of the RA prior to marginal contact occurring with Ingram (NOP) as Ingram slips the contact during the dunk attempt.
Porter Jr. (HOU) moves into and delivers body contact to Alvarado (NOP) and affects Alvarado's SQBR.
